<section xml:id="_introduction">
<title>Introduction</title>
<simpara>Boat is a set of core Java/Kotlin libraries (JDK 1.8+), mostly written by kotlin, widely used on JVM projects within <link xl:href="https://github.com/srclab-projects">SrcLab</link>.
It provides many fast and convenient interfaces, functions and utilities.</simpara>
<simpara>Boat includes:</simpara>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-annotations/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-annotations</link>: Core annotations;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-core/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-core</link>: Core lib;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-serialize/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-serialize</link>: Serialization and deserialization lib (supports <literal>JSON</literal>);</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-codec/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-codec</link>: Codec lib (supports <literal>HEX</literal>, <literal>BASE64</literal>, <literal>SHA</literal>, <literal>MD</literal>, <literal>HMAC</literal>, <literal>AES</literal>, <literal>RSA</literal>, <literal>SM2</literal>, etc.);</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-id/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-id</link>: Fast ID generation lib;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-others/DOCUMENTATION.md">boat-others</link>: Third party supporting and extension lib (such as <literal>protobuf</literal>);</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-test/">boat-test</link>: Testing libs dependencies management project;</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat-bom/">boat-bom</link>: BOM (gradle platform) project;</simpara>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
<simpara>If you want to import common jars at once (<literal>annotations</literal>, <literal>core</literal>, <literal>codec</literal>, <literal>serialize</literal> and <literal>id</literal>), just import:</simpara>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara><link xl:href="../boat/">boat</link>.</simpara>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</section>
<section xml:id="_getting">
<title>Getting</title>
<section xml:id="_get_boat">
<title>Get Boat</title>
<formalpara>
<title>Gradle</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="groovy" linenumbering="unnumbered">implementation "xyz.srclab.common:boat:0.0.1"</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>Maven</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="xml" linenumbering="unnumbered">&lt;dependency&gt;
  &lt;groupId&gt;xyz.srclab.common&lt;/groupId&gt;
  &lt;artifactId&gt;boat&lt;/artifactId&gt;
  &lt;version&gt;0.0.1&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
</section>
<section xml:id="_with_bom">
<title>With BOM</title>
<formalpara>
<title>Gradle</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="groovy" linenumbering="unnumbered">api implementation("xyz.srclab.common:boat-bom:0.0.1")</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>Maven</title>
<para>
<programlisting language="xml" linenumbering="unnumbered">&lt;dependencyManagement&gt;
  &lt;dependencies&gt;
    &lt;dependency&gt;
      &lt;groupId&gt;xyz.srclab.common&lt;/groupId&gt;
      &lt;artifactId&gt;boat&lt;/artifactId&gt;
      &lt;version&gt;0.0.1&lt;/version&gt;
      &lt;type&gt;pom&lt;/type&gt;
      &lt;scope&gt;import&lt;/scope&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;
  &lt;/dependencies&gt;
&lt;/dependencyManagement&gt;</programlisting>
</para>
</formalpara>
